description: Demolition of existing buildings. Erection of a 3-5 storey building and a 6-7 storey building providing 679sqm of retail and 331sqm of office space at ground floor level, 81 flats and 2 No 2 storey houses with associated amenity space and basement parking. Main amendments include increased setback from railway line to create additional public realm, alterations to design of buildings/ space to rear and alterations to number/ mix of residential units, amount of commercial floorspace and alterations to access ramp/ basement to provide a total of 42 car parking spaces
